Package com.sun.enterprise.annotations

Annotation Types Summary
Contract Marker annotation for interfaces that represent a contract that will be implemented by services.
Provides Annotation marks instances of object which are labeled as exported by a component.
Requires Annotation to define a required resource for a componnent.
Service Marker interface for service implementation.
